WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.550
Hey, good morning family. Thank you for

00:00:02.560 --> 00:00:04.789
joining me today. Well, a lot

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:06.470
of people don't agree with the baptism of

00:00:06.480 --> 00:00:08.629
the Holy Spirit—I see it in the

00:00:08.639 --> 00:00:10.790
emails and everything—but listen,

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.709
this is my channel and I'm led by the

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:14.549
Holy Spirit in what He's told me to do.

00:00:14.559 --> 00:00:16.710
I'm going to pray in the baptism

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:17.990
of the Holy Spirit. I'm going to pray in

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.150
tongues without an interpreter. I

00:00:20.160 --> 00:00:23.029
believe if you are in

00:00:23.039 --> 00:00:25.509
your private setting at home, or if

00:00:25.519 --> 00:00:27.189
I'm making a video for the

00:00:27.199 --> 00:00:29.669
internet, I can pray in tongues. Now, if I'm

00:00:29.679 --> 00:00:31.990
in a church service and I just burst out

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:33.510
in tongues and start praying, there

00:00:33.520 --> 00:00:35.190
needs to be an interpreter or you need to

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.470
be quiet. Just like people are telling

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:38.709
me, 'You need to be

00:00:38.709 --> 00:00:38.719
quiet.'No,

00:00:38.719 --> 00:00:40.950
I'm not in a church

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.869
service; I'm not disrupting anything.

00:00:42.879 --> 00:00:44.310
If I were to pray out

00:00:44.310 --> 00:00:44.320
loud

00:00:44.320 --> 00:00:46.150
in a church service while the pastor is talking, there

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:49.029
would

00:00:49.039 --> 00:00:51.029
need

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:52.549
to be an interpretation of

00:00:52.549 --> 00:00:52.559
those

00:00:52.559 --> 00:00:55.830
tongues or it would be disruptive

00:00:55.830 --> 00:00:55.840
and

00:00:55.840 --> 00:00:58.310
confusing. There should be a

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:00.150
balance to everything. But when I'm

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:03.270
praying in the Spirit in my house

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:06.310
to the Father with an unknown tongue,

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:08.950
praying forth mysteries out

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.270
of my spirit, I'm praying to Him and the

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:13.630
Holy Spirit prays through me a perfect

00:01:13.630 --> 00:01:13.640
prayer—a

00:01:13.640 --> 00:01:16.469
perfect prayer that always

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:18.789
hits the target. I'm going to move

00:01:18.789 --> 00:01:18.799
on from

00:01:18.799 --> 00:01:19.990
that; I'm not going to keep going

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:21.590
down that road. If you don't agree,

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:23.030
click out of the video. That's the bottom

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.710
line. This

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:26.550
is something else: When you're driving

00:01:26.560 --> 00:01:29.590
down the road and

00:01:29.590 --> 00:01:29.600
someone's

00:01:29.600 --> 00:01:32.149
face comes before you—maybe it's your

00:01:32.159 --> 00:01:34.870
in-laws, your family,

00:01:34.880 --> 00:01:37.190
your husband, or your

00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:37.200
wife—and

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:40.149
it just comes out of nowhere, pray in the

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:43.510
Spirit concerning what you're seeing. I

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:45.670
believe a lot of times the Holy Spirit

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:48.469
will come to us and warn us with

00:01:48.479 --> 00:01:51.990
pictures like that, saying, 'Hey, you

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.109
need to pray for your

00:01:53.109 --> 00:01:53.119
daughter,'or

00:01:53.119 --> 00:01:54.789
your son. It's a warning. You may

00:01:54.799 --> 00:01:56.590
not have thought of that person for

00:01:56.600 --> 00:01:59.270
years, and they just come up in you, and

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:00.870
you're like, 'I remember Sister

00:02:00.870 --> 00:02:00.880
So-and-so.'Those

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:04.709
could be prayer cues for you to

00:02:04.719 --> 00:02:07.109
intercede on behalf of that individual

00:02:07.119 --> 00:02:09.350
you're thinking about.

00:02:09.350 --> 00:02:09.360
Even

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:11.029
if

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:13.030
you haven't thought about them in decades,

00:02:13.030 --> 00:02:13.040
if

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:14.869
all of a sudden they

00:02:14.879 --> 00:02:17.030
come up before you,

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:19.270
start praying in the Spirit for that.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:21.270
A lot of times, the Holy

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:23.190
Spirit will give us cues like

00:02:23.190 --> 00:02:23.200
that—it

00:02:23.200 --> 00:02:24.949
could be for the president or

00:02:24.949 --> 00:02:24.959
many other

00:02:24.959 --> 00:02:27.670
things. Or if

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:30.110
you're driving and you feel a

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:33.110
caution, like something is not

00:02:33.110 --> 00:02:33.120
right—you

00:02:33.120 --> 00:02:35.750
can't put your finger on

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:39.350
it, but you feel an urgency to pray for

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:40.670
so-and-so.

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:43.750
Intercede in the Spirit for that

00:02:43.760 --> 00:02:45.670
individual.

00:02:45.670 --> 00:02:45.680
Many

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:48.150
times, the Holy Spirit will take that and

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:50.309
you'll go 'into

00:02:50.309 --> 00:02:50.319
the river.'You

00:02:50.319 --> 00:02:53.270
can tell when it's dry prayer versus

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:55.190
Holy Ghost prayer. When Holy Ghost

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:56.869
prayer gets in there, you can

00:02:56.879 --> 00:02:58.390
just keep praying.

00:02:58.390 --> 00:02:58.400
Sometimes

00:02:58.400 --> 00:03:00.229
it's

00:03:00.239 --> 00:03:02.869
dry, but then all

00:03:02.879 --> 00:03:05.270
of a sudden you'll hit a 'gusher,'as

00:03:05.270 --> 00:03:05.280
I

00:03:05.280 --> 00:03:07.190
call it—a Holy Ghost

00:03:07.190 --> 00:03:07.200
river—and

00:03:07.200 --> 00:03:09.670
you

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:11.750
can feel it bubbling out of you.

00:03:11.760 --> 00:03:15.110
The more you pray in tongues, the

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:18.070
more you develop your spirit. The more

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.750
you do this over and over again—like

00:03:19.750 --> 00:03:19.760
going

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:22.550
to the

00:03:22.550 --> 00:03:22.560
gym—you

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:26.229
jump in these rivers.

00:03:26.239 --> 00:03:28.710
I have learned that what used to

00:03:28.720 --> 00:03:31.030
take a long time to get into those

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:33.190
flows... it felt like

00:03:33.200 --> 00:03:35.589
pushing a weight down the

00:03:35.599 --> 00:03:38.149
road or like

00:03:38.149 --> 00:03:38.159
tilling

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:41.430
sawdust.

00:03:41.440 --> 00:03:43.350
You're tilling

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:45.430
and tilling, and then all of a sudden you go 'boom'and

00:03:45.430 --> 00:03:45.440
you

00:03:45.440 --> 00:03:47.270
flow.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:51.030
The more

00:03:51.040 --> 00:03:53.430
you pray in the Spirit, the more you

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:55.670
develop it and the easier it gets to get into

00:03:55.670 --> 00:03:55.680
those

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.149
rivers. That's what we're all

00:03:58.159 --> 00:04:01.910
looking for. Dry prayer time is

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:04.869
a drag. Seriously, when you're

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:06.229
praying in the Spirit and

00:04:06.239 --> 00:04:08.789
it's dry, it’s tough, but

00:04:08.799 --> 00:04:10.869
eventually, the more you develop your

00:04:10.879 --> 00:04:12.789
tongues and

00:04:12.789 --> 00:04:12.799
your

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.309
spirit, the faster you'll jump in

00:04:14.309 --> 00:04:14.319
those

00:04:14.319 --> 00:04:17.110
rivers.

00:04:17.120 --> 00:04:19.349
Sometimes it takes two

00:04:19.349 --> 00:04:19.359
or

00:04:19.359 --> 00:04:21.469
four minutes, and you can

00:04:21.479 --> 00:04:25.110
tell there is a definite shift

00:04:25.110 --> 00:04:25.120
when

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:27.749
you hit those rivers. You know you're

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:29.670
praying and getting downloads

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.110
from the Spirit of the Lord.

00:04:31.120 --> 00:04:32.550
That's what He was talking about

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:35.310
yesterday: it's a

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:37.469
dance. Don't rush

00:04:37.479 --> 00:04:41.830
it. We often try to

00:04:41.830 --> 00:04:41.840
rush

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:44.230
because we don't want to take the

00:04:44.230 --> 00:04:44.240
time—and

00:04:44.240 --> 00:04:46.950
I know He's rebuking me, too.

00:04:46.950 --> 00:04:46.960
We

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:48.629
don't want to take the time

00:04:48.639 --> 00:04:50.950
on a certain area, but

00:04:50.960 --> 00:04:54.310
it's a dance. You let Him lead and

00:04:54.320 --> 00:04:57.830
you follow, dancing with

00:04:57.840 --> 00:04:59.830
the tongues and the

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:02.469
prayer. You let the Holy

00:05:02.479 --> 00:05:04.790
Spirit lead you, and He will guide you

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:07.670
into all things. That's

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:09.590
what happens when you start praying

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:11.909
in the Spirit: you let the Holy Spirit

00:05:11.919 --> 00:05:13.990
lead you. Sometimes it feels like

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:17.830
there's no direction, but

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:20.230
I know this: the more you pray and

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:22.230
yield, worshiping

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:24.390
Him and thanking Him,

00:05:24.400 --> 00:05:25.990
all of a sudden He'll start

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:27.350
giving cues. 'I want you to go this

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:30.070
direction.'I

00:05:31.919 --> 00:05:33.749
hope that helped you a

00:05:33.759 --> 00:05:36.310
little bit because it helps me.

00:05:36.310 --> 00:05:36.320
When

00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:37.909
you're learning

00:05:37.919 --> 00:05:39.870
this stuff and nobody's teaching it at the

00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:42.469
churches—unless

00:05:42.479 --> 00:05:44.390
you find an old CD

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:47.270
or tape series—you can

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:52.790
go back and listen to some of the

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:56.790
old Hagin prayer videos

00:05:56.800 --> 00:05:58.550
about praying in the

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:00.710
Spirit, learn how to flow with the

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:03.590
Holy Ghost with Rick and

00:06:03.590 --> 00:06:03.600
Denise Renner, and

00:06:03.600 --> 00:06:05.510
some of the greats like

00:06:05.510 --> 00:06:05.520
Jeanie

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:07.749
Wilkerson. Learn how to

00:06:07.759 --> 00:06:09.990
flow in the Spirit when you pray. I

00:06:09.990 --> 00:06:10.000
believe

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:11.510
what I

00:06:11.510 --> 00:06:11.520
gave you

00:06:11.520 --> 00:06:13.670
will help a

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.270
little bit. I don't

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:17.189
necessarily feel I teach all

00:06:17.199 --> 00:06:19.510
that great, but I have had the

00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:22.469
opportunity to sit in the shadows of

00:06:22.479 --> 00:06:25.110
some really amazing prayer warriors over

00:06:25.120 --> 00:06:28.469
the years. God's put me there

00:06:28.469 --> 00:06:28.479
with

00:06:28.479 --> 00:06:31.909
mentors who have

00:06:31.919 --> 00:06:34.469
really changed my life. Through the

00:06:34.479 --> 00:06:37.270
impartations of sitting and listening to

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:40.870
them pray, I've learned a lot

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:40.880
that

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:43.110
I don't even realize I know.

00:06:43.110 --> 00:06:43.120
Many

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:45.350
people on YouTube do

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:47.909
not know these things. I

00:06:47.919 --> 00:06:49.270
feel like everyone knows them, but

00:06:49.270 --> 00:06:49.280
many

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:50.710
people

00:06:50.720 --> 00:06:53.590
don't do them. So, I tell you what I

00:06:53.600 --> 00:06:55.990
know

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:58.950
as the Lord brings it to me.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.710
Thank you

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:03.350
for being here, and

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.950
we'll pray it out together today.

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:08.990
Father, we just yield to

00:07:09.000 --> 00:07:12.309
You. You lead, Father, and we

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:13.070
will

00:07:13.080 --> 00:07:15.270
follow. We're not in a

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:17.830
hurry. We sit at Your feet and we

00:07:17.840 --> 00:07:20.870
thank You, Holy Spirit, that You pray

00:07:20.880 --> 00:07:24.230
through us. It's not flesh prayer;

00:07:24.240 --> 00:07:26.550
it's Holy Ghost prayer.

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:30.150
Father, pray through us as we lift up our

00:07:30.160 --> 00:07:31.390
voice

00:07:31.390 --> 00:07:31.400
and

00:07:31.400 --> 00:07:35.350
yield our spirit to You. We

00:07:35.360 --> 00:07:37.589
thank You, Lord, that You would pray

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:39.909
whatever You have need of—whatever is

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:41.350
going on in this earth—and that we could

00:07:41.360 --> 00:07:43.510
help by praying and

00:07:43.510 --> 00:07:43.520
loosing

00:07:43.520 --> 00:07:45.189
and binding.

00:07:45.199 --> 00:07:48.790
Father, we yield

00:07:48.790 --> 00:07:48.800
ourselves

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:51.990
to You right now in the name of Jesus.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:54.230
Now, Father, I truly do not have a

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.749
direction other than that we could pray

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:57.430
about a lot of things, but I don't

00:07:57.440 --> 00:07:59.670
want to just pray what's on my thoughts;

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:02.230
I want to pray what's on Your heart. What

00:08:02.230 --> 00:08:02.240
is

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:04.710
the heartbeat of the Father today

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:07.670
for us? So, we'll start out, I'll

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:08.950
pray in the Spirit, and

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:11.110
we'll just take our time here and

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:13.350
figure it out.

00:08:13.360 --> 00:08:15.990
It's like one of those old hunting dogs.

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:19.189
He'll get the scent of

00:08:19.199 --> 00:08:21.670
the prey of what we're supposed to.

00:08:21.680 --> 00:08:22.869
You know what I'm saying? And we'll find

00:08:22.879 --> 00:08:25.350
it by just sniff around. That's a

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:27.430
good way to say it, huh? Well, if we

00:08:27.440 --> 00:08:28.950
just sniff around a little bit, we'll

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:30.869
find it. Just like a little

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:34.310
dog or a or a bird dog, you know? We'll

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:52.110
find it. So, Father, we just thank

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:55.509
you. Holy Spirit, we thank you. Holy

00:08:55.519 --> 00:09:27.990
Spirit we yield.

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:30.389
I think it should always be a staple. I

00:09:30.399 --> 00:09:32.350
just always hear him say, "Take

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:36.870
communion when we go in before the Lord.

00:09:36.880 --> 00:09:39.110
We take communion before we go before

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:41.350
him and and and and go in by the blood

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:43.750
of the lamb, by the word. And Father, we

00:09:43.760 --> 00:09:46.310
thank you, Lord, for the body. We thank

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.949
you, Lord, that you were wounded for our

00:09:47.959 --> 00:09:49.829
transgressions. You were bruised for our

00:09:49.839 --> 00:09:52.389
iniquities. The chastisement of our

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:55.350
peace was upon you, and with your

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:58.310
stripes were healed. And we have divine

00:09:58.320 --> 00:10:01.190
health. We have divine health. And what

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.590
you bore in your body, we'll not bear in

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.509
our own. We thank you, Lord, that you

00:10:05.519 --> 00:10:07.990
took it all for us. And our me our

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.310
mental, our

00:10:09.320 --> 00:10:11.509
emotions, people are dealing with all

00:10:11.519 --> 00:10:14.470
kinds of PTSD, all of it. It doesn't

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:16.790
matter. You You have night terrors, all

00:10:16.800 --> 00:10:19.670
of it. Jesus paid the price for you to

00:10:19.680 --> 00:10:22.230
walk in victory. And I thank you, Lord,

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.870
that as we take this body, we take it in

00:10:24.880 --> 00:10:27.829
the name of Jesus, and we say, Jesus,

00:10:27.839 --> 00:10:29.670
thank you for taking all that on your

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:31.750
body for us. And we don't have to take

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:34.069
it on our body. You're good to us, Lord,

00:10:34.079 --> 00:10:35.829
and we're thankful for all that you've

00:10:35.839 --> 00:10:37.630
done in

00:10:37.630 --> 00:10:37.640
Jesus'name.

00:10:37.640 --> 00:10:41.030
Now, Lord, we lift up the blood

00:10:41.040 --> 00:10:43.670
and we apply the blood of Jesus. For we

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:45.190
make much of the blood and the blood

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:48.870
makes much of us. And you said, "If

00:10:48.880 --> 00:10:50.790
we confess our sins, you're faithful and

00:10:50.800 --> 00:10:52.710
just to forgive us of our sins and

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:54.630
cleanse us from all

00:10:54.630 --> 00:10:54.640
unrighteousness."And

00:10:54.640 --> 00:10:56.630
we take this blood right now in the

00:10:56.640 --> 00:10:58.310
name of Jesus and we apply it to our

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:01.910
life.

00:11:01.920 --> 00:11:04.910
Thank you, Lord. Thank you,

00:11:04.920 --> 00:11:07.750
Father. You're so good to us, Father.

00:11:07.760 --> 00:11:09.990
You're so good to us, Father. Thank you,

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:13.150
Father, for all that you've

00:11:13.160 --> 00:11:16.310
done. Thank you, Father. You've been

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:21.550
good to us,

00:11:21.560 --> 00:11:24.750
Father. We enter into your throne room

00:11:24.760 --> 00:11:28.630
boldly. We're not abandoned, we are adopted.

00:11:28.640 --> 00:11:30.870
We're joint-heirs with you

00:11:30.880 --> 00:11:33.190
because of what you did for us. And we

